sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant D as Dashboard
    participant A as API (Fastify)
    participant R as Runtime
    participant AG as Agents
    participant LLM as LLM Adapter<br/>(OpenRouter)
    participant MEM as Memory
    participant BUS as EventBus
    participant OTEL as OpenTelemetry

    U->>D: open dashboard
    D->>A: GET /health
    A-->>D: 200 {status:ok}
    A->>OTEL: start span "api.health"
    A-->>OTEL: end span

    U->>D: click "Run workflow"
    D->>A: POST /v1/workflows/:id/run
    A->>R: invoke(runId)
    R->>OTEL: start span "workflow.execute"

    loop per step
        R->>AG: invoke(agentId, input)
        AG->>LLM: stream(model, prompt)
        LLM-->>AG: tokens (SSE)
        AG-->>R: result

        opt step needs memory
            R->>MEM: put(namespace, key, value)
            MEM-->>R: ack
            R->>MEM: get(namespace, key)
            MEM-->>R: value
        end

        R->>BUS: publish(step.completed)
        BUS-->>D: streaming sub (Phase 2)
    end

    R-->>A: run finished
    R->>OTEL: end span
    A-->>D: 200 {runId, status:completed}
    D-->>U: render result
